# Three services — shared intake data model

Same Supabase project (`cgghmctyygkqzalfhqsx`) for iep-user-dashboard and sustainable-website.

## Survey source of truth

**`lead_magnets.metadata.intake_answers`** — not a separate survey table.

- Join to appointments by email (`metadata.email` / `intake_answers.contact_email`)
- IEP portal dashboards may also read **`portal_iep_profiles`** after enrollment — that is profile overlay, not the intake questionnaire store

## Do not

- Create service-specific duplicate tables for intake answers
- Assume IEP-only schema when building generic dashboard APIs

Full conventions: `../sustainable-website/.cursor/rules/shared-intake-data-model.mdc`
